snippet.title: Interloper Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Interloper is a fast-paced real-time strategy game with matches that take only 5 minutes. By predicting your opponent's movements, you corner them to claim the entire map. 
http://interlopergame.com
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/356420
